{"tid":1737630,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動post-行動代號21000730]星期六晚9點前返屋企訓教，星期日730等票站開門","createTime":"2019-11-19T04:13:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T09:23:22.000Z","uid":7807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b5fb4fde453c42eb44a462d3f62b84579e2dd54e","tid":1737630,"uid":7807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔理星期六發生咩事都好！全城灰姑娘！全城9點前要返屋企訓教！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你張床要人！你老婆要人！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然政府未必咁大膽突然提早關閉票站，但我地都無理由冒呢個風險！而且如果太夜去投，係會大排長龍，大夜訓又唔好既！<br />\n<br />\n但如果大家早去而大排長龍，就無問題喇，係可惜啲<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">老人家就同你班後生一齊排，我就唔知佢地有無體力同你班後生排到咁耐。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以要早起身，就一定要早啲訓，打少晚機，打少晚飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時間</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">票站開朝早7點半，一於有秩序地排隊等投票！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n務求中午12點前，大家都完成投票去飲早茶食飯！大家亦不妨約埋老豆老母一齊投票飲茶做孝子！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">衣著</span></span><br />\n你著咩衫關我撚事，你平時出街食飯著咩衫？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">場外投票調查</span></span><br />\n同埋你無需向任何人透露你既投票意向！<br />\n但你係都要講既，唔好誤導人地，這樣是不對的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係支持建制既咪講囉，你係支持偽中立，你咪講囉。但都係果句，唔係建議大家去透露，唔講係正常既！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推post</span></span><br />\n呢個post慢慢推，唔急，仲有幾日，最緊要有毅力！呢個星期出面仲有好多事值得大家關注！"},{"pid":"1811210fab48402f8e30927be312c157f71ead06","tid":1737630,"uid":7807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"開頭都係靠自己推住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1cdfd56f291722b44163f02504623d9740b4ed","tid":1737630,"uid":7807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23eab7dbae6847c4e4bb2ba34f92f3d4fd0412c6","tid":1737630,"uid":7807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:27:34.000Z","msg":"夠5個reply要幫幫我手推一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"750fa2e32c96d130570aa2dfcd4b3715f2f7282c","tid":1737630,"uid":7807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:39:18.000Z","msg":"1) 選票上等印仔乾哂先對摺，確保選票只有一個印喺一個候選人上<br />\n2) 留意今年好多候選人扮獨立，就算寫咗五大訴求、缺一不可都未必係真泛民，小心俾人攤薄泛民票<br />\n3) 選票上唔好寫任何嘢，唔係張票就會DQ<br />\n<br />\n 一位之前係票站主任的溫馨提示：<br />\n投票吸印仔後，吹下佢，㕶好即刻對摺，驚個「剔」印埋落對面果頁，我會行埋到票箱先摺，因為真係印左落對面果頁，一票兩個「剔」會成為廢票。她見好多上述情況，尤其早上，因個印仔仲好濕。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n重有, 睇清楚張票有冇損毀, 少少爛都會當廢票！"},{"pid":"217ce298bdfed24b47d5040b2eba53326147560c","tid":1737630,"uid":339387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"同路人，撐"},{"pid":"fe3525b8a52800d21aa2330aeb73fc28c3a607e6","tid":1737630,"uid":7807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T09:23:22.000Z","msg":"又夠鐘推下"}]}